<hgroup><h1>Burden of Ischemic and Hemorrhagic Stroke Across the US From 1990 to 2019</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Renedo%20D"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Daniela Renedo</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Daniela Renedo</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Neurology, Yale School of Medicine, New Haven, Connecticut</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Neurosurgery, Yale School of Medicine, New Haven, Connecticut</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Renedo%20D"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Daniela Renedo</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Acosta%20JN"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Julian N Acosta</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Julian N Acosta</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Neurology, Yale School of Medicine, New Haven, Connecticut</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Acosta%20JN"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Julian N Acosta</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Leasure%20AC"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Audrey C Leasure</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Audrey C Leasure</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Neurology, Yale School of Medicine, New Haven, Connecticut</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Leasure%20AC"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Audrey C Leasure</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Sharma%20R"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Richa Sharma</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Richa Sharma</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
